==============================
|ID|OPERATOR          |NAME  |
------------------------------
|0 |NESTED-LOOP JOIN  |      |
|1 |├─TABLE FULL SCAN |t2    |
|2 |└─TABLE RANGE SCAN|t1(i1)|
==============================
